ze< 100}))\n(m/bind #'get-user {mc/tags [:user]} my-cache)\n```\n\n## Cache Configuration Options\n\nThese settings control the cache itself. Use vars from `memento.config` (aliased as `mc`).\n\n### `mc/type` (Required)\n\nCache implementation type. **You must specify this for caching to work.**\n\n```clojure\n{mc/type mc/caffeine}  ; High-performance Caffeine cache",
